Class PrefixComparator

java.lang.Object
org.apache.spark.util.collection.unsafe.sort.PrefixComparator
Direct Known Subclasses:
PrefixComparators.RadixSortSupport
@Private public abstract class PrefixComparator extends Object
Compares 8-byte key prefixes in prefix sort. Subclasses may implement type-specific comparisons, such as lexicographic comparison for strings.
